{"id": "iqk1665702595933", "title": "$editmode", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Functions", "$editmode"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iqk1665702595933.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">$editmode</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous:   $e \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous:   $e \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cab1719662668520.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next:   $empty \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next:   $empty \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kdx1665702752335.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/iqk1665702595933.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/iqk1665702595933.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/iqk1665702595933.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528656\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528656\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104iqk1665702595933.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iqk1665702595933.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iqk1665702595933.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"iqk1665702595933\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $editmode\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"iqk1665702595933___editmode_260351\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return or set a value that determines the degree to which a user can change data on the form component.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__topic_d82274e1_d82275e1_d82276e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__p_d82277e1_d82278e1_d82279e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Return</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$editmode</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__p_d82280e1_d82281e1_d82282e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$editmode</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__topic_d54307e1_d54308e1_d54309e1_d54310e1_d54311e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1015907e90\">\n                       \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8357e1_d8358e1_d8359e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8357e1_d8358e1_d8359e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8357e1_d8358e1_d8359e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8357e1_d8358e1_d8359e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8357e1_d8358e1_d8359e1__entry__2\">\n Edit mode—the form can be used for all I/O purposes. Values can be retrieved and changed by the user.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8357e1_d8358e1_d8359e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8357e1_d8358e1_d8359e1__entry__2\">\n Query mode— the form can only be used only for query purposes. Values can be entered as profile data, but retrieved values cannot be modified.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8357e1_d8358e1_d8359e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">2</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8357e1_d8358e1_d8359e1__entry__2\">\n Display mode—the form is read-only, and values cannot be entered by the user.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__topic_d54312e1_d54313e1_d54314e1_d54315e1_d54316e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1015907e166\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__p_d82289e1_d82290e1_d82291e1\">Returns the current value, which may be the initial value set by Uniface when the form was activated or a value set in ProcScript using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$editmode</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__p_d82292e1_d82293e1_d82294e1\">The initial value for <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$editmode</span> is determined by how the form was activated and displayed:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8360e1_d8361e1_d8362e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Initial values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$editmode</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8360e1_d8361e1_d8362e1__entry__1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8360e1_d8361e1_d8362e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8360e1_d8361e1_d8362e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8360e1_d8361e1_d8362e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The form is in edit mode. <var class=\"keyword varname\">All</var> the following conditions are met:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__li_d34037e1_d34038e1_d34039e1\">The form was started by one of these methods:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__li_d34040e1_d34041e1_d34042e1\">With an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">activate</span> statement (resulting in an implicit <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span>).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__li_d34043e1_d34044e1_d34045e1\">With a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> statement used with the component instance properties <code class=\"ph codeph\">DISPLAY=FALSE</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">QUERY=FALSE</code>.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__li_d34046e1_d34047e1_d34048e1\">The form becomes active with an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span> statement, or if the exec operation is empty (implicit <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span>).\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__li_d34049e1_d34050e1_d34051e1\">The form's <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Data Access</span> property is set to a value other than <code class=\"ph codeph\">L (read-only)</code>.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8360e1_d8361e1_d8362e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8360e1_d8361e1_d8362e1__entry__2\">The form is in query mode. It was started by a\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> statement, with the component instance\n                        property <code class=\"ph codeph\">QUERY=TRUE</code>, or it was started with an\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">activate</span> statement and the following conditions were\n                        met: <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__li_d34052e1_d34053e1_d34054e1\">The form's <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Data\n                                 Access</span> property is set to a value other than <code class=\"ph codeph\">L\n                                 (read-only)</code>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__li_d34055e1_d34056e1_d34057e1\">The form becomes active with an\n                                 <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span> statement, or if the exec operation is\n                              empty (implicit <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">edit</span>). </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8360e1_d8361e1_d8362e1__entry__1\">\n 2\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iqk1665702595933__table_d8360e1_d8361e1_d8362e1__entry__2\">\n The form is in display mode and is read-only. One of these conditions is met:\n <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__li_d34058e1_d34059e1_d34060e1\">The form was started with a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> statement used with the component instance property <code class=\"ph codeph\">DISPLAY=TRUE</code>.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__li_d34061e1_d34062e1_d34063e1\">The form becomes active with a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">display</span> statement.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__topic_d54317e1_d54318e1_d54319e1_d54320e1_d54321e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1015907e347\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__d5909e20\">Use in Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__topic_d54322e1_d54323e1_d54324e1_d54325e1_d54326e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1015907e357\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__p_d82304e1_d82305e1_d82306e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$editmode</span> function returns or\n            sets the degree to which a user can change data on the form component. Setting\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$editmode</span> has immediate effect.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__section_lpy_qh5_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1015907e378\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$editmode</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example informs the user as to whether the form is\n               editable or read-only.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__pre_zvm_rh5_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\nselectcase $editmode\n case 0\n message/info \"This form is editable\"\nelsecase\n message/info \"This form is not editable\"\n endselectcase\nedit\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__section_ekx_lh5_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1015907e395\">Example: Setting Form to Display Mode </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example starts a form in display mode:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__pre_zfm_4h5_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation displayCustomer\n; Start display mode for this form.\n $editmode = 2 ; DISPLAY\n edit/modal\nend\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__section_gnf_lh5_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1015907e410\">Example: Changing from Edit Mode to Display Mode </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows how to change from edit mode to display\n               mode:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"iqk1665702595933__pre_zgp_lh5_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation doStore\n ;- store the data and\n ;- keep the user from making any more changes.\n store\n ;- TODO: error trapping ...\n $editmode = 2 ; DISPLAY\nend\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gwk1665702595783.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>edit</a><p>Display the component in preparation for user input.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/epe1665702596013.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$interactive</a><p>Return a boolean value indicating whether the current Form component is in interactive state.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryt1665702577808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>newinstance</a><p>Creates a new instance of a component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528656\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528656\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$editmode Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $editmode Return or set a value that determines the degree to which a user can change data on the form component. Return = $editmode $editmode = 0 | 1 | 2 Arguments Value Meaning 0 Edit mode—the form can be used for all I/O purposes. Values can be retrieved and changed by the user. 1 Query mode— the form can only be used only for query purposes. Values can be entered as profile data, but retrieved values cannot be modified. 2 Display mode—the form is read-only, and values cannot be entered by the user. Return Values Returns the current value, which may be the initial value set by Uniface when the form was activated or a value set in ProcScript using $editmode . The initial value for $editmode is determined by how the form was activated and displayed: Table 1. Initial values returned by $editmode Value Meaning 0 The form is in edit mode. All the following conditions are met: The form was started by one of these methods: With an activate statement (resulting in an implicit newinstance ). With a newinstance statement used with the component instance properties DISPLAY=FALSE and QUERY=FALSE . The form becomes active with an edit statement, or if the exec operation is empty (implicit edit ). The form's Data Access property is set to a value other than L (read-only) . 1 The form is in query mode. It was started by a newinstance statement, with the component instance property QUERY=TRUE , or it was started with an activate statement and the following conditions were met: The form's Data Access property is set to a value other than L (read-only) . The form becomes active with an edit statement, or if the exec operation is empty (implicit edit ). 2 The form is in display mode and is read-only. One of these conditions is met: The form was started with a newinstance statement used with the component instance property DISPLAY=TRUE . The form becomes active with a display statement. Use Use in Form components. Description The $editmode function returns or sets the degree to which a user can change data on the form component. Setting $editmode has immediate effect. Example: Using $editmode The following example informs the user as to whether the form is editable or read-only. operation exec selectcase $editmode case 0 message/info \"This form is editable\" elsecase message/info \"This form is not editable\" endselectcase edit end; exec Copy Example: Setting Form to Display Mode The following example starts a form in display mode: operation displayCustomer ; Start display mode for this form. $editmode = 2 ; DISPLAY edit/modal end Copy Example: Changing from Edit Mode to Display Mode The following example shows how to change from edit mode to display mode: operation doStore ;- store the data and ;- keep the user from making any more changes. store ;- TODO: error trapping ... $editmode = 2 ; DISPLAY end Copy Related Links edit Display the component in preparation for user input. $interactive Return a boolean value indicating whether the current Form component is in interactive state. newinstance Creates a new instance of a component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}